{"tid":2433339,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"YouTube指若暴力風險降低將恢復川普帳號","createTime":"2021-03-05T01:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T01:07:14.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"da3ed9ac0a641693560b0f0380538d5dcbd41b17","tid":2433339,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:05:49.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國前總統川普的社群平台帳號幾乎全數被封鎖，與外界互動顯得較為不易，但最近終於有一線曙光，YouTube指出，只要確定暴力風險消失，將會恢復川普的帳號。<br />\n<br />\n《CNN》報導，YouTube執行長沃斯基（Susan Wojcicki）指出，YouTube會依據一系列的指標來評估暴力風險，指標包括政府官員的聲明、執法的層級、YouTube上的暴力言論。但她也說目前無法確定何時會恢復川普的帳號，由於本週美國國會仍遭到潛在的暴力威脅，因此川普帳號仍處於暫停狀態，沃斯基說「很明顯地，現在暴力風險還很高」<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456865&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUridffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=45bbb1fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456865&h=cb4eb31f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456865</a>"},{"pid":"254d2b54cff0c7f4c8feedcd4508d83b5963d5a5","tid":2433339,"uid":60635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T01:07:14.000Z","msg":"國家安全部- YOUTUBE分部<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/medicine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}